        <item>
            <title>Version 2.0.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 15:23:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Seed 2.0.0</h2>
                <ul>
                  <li><b>Notes open in place</b> — a note expands right where it sits in the list and collapses back when you close it.</li>
                  <li><b>Version history</b> — see how a note grew, read any past version, revert with one click.</li>
                  <li><b>Garden Backup</b> — point a garden at a folder and Seed keeps one complete, safe copy automatically.</li>
                </ul>
                <p><a href="https://procestra.app/seed-releases.html">See everything in 2.0.0</a></p>
            ]]></description>
