                <h2>Seed 1.0.2</h2>
                <ul>
                  <li><b>Recent gardens</b> — the Open Garden menu now lists gardens you've used recently.</li>
                  <li><b>Tidier New menu</b> — New, Open Garden, and Close Garden are grouped together.</li>
                  <li><b>Safer saves</b> — fixes that keep edits from being lost when notes reload or are restored from the trash.</li>
